se.cbb.jprime.prm

Class Dependencies

  • java.lang.Object
    • se.cbb.jprime.prm.Dependencies
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Dependencies>

    public class Dependencies
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Dependencies>
    Container to collect all PRM dependencies for a single child attribute. Two instances of this class containing equal (or rather identical) internal dependencies are considered equal. The number of internal dependencies may be 0, i.e. parent-less instances are allowed.
    Author:
